      News story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    UK Government-supported mass Covid-19 testing begins in Merthyr
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">UK Military provides logistical support for county-wide programme of testing.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
